query: SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.username, u.userType, u.loginMethod, u.createdAt, d.id as distributor_id, d.distributorCode, d.username as dist_username, d.status, d.rank, d.isActive FROM users u LEFT JOIN distributors d ON u.id = d.userId;
